<refsection condition="ref.description">
<title>Description</title>

<para>A <tag>hardware</tag> element identifies some physical component
of a computer system. Even though DocBook provides a broad range of
inlines for describing the various software components of a system, it
provides relatively few for describing hardware.
</para>
<para>If you need to identify a number of different hardware components,
you may wish to consider extending DocBook, or at least using the
<tag class="attribute">role</tag> attribute to further classify
<tag>hardware</tag>.
</para>

